data.description: Step into this inviting split-level 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home.  Basement with garage access, the backyard is fenced in for added privacy. This property is able to give you the blank canvas, to add your own creative touch! This property has the convenience of high-speed fiber optic internet. Located just moments away from the charming Town of Wardensville. Positioned less than 30 minutes from Winchester, Virginia, and under two hours from Washington, DC. Schedule your showing today! *Property is being sold AS-IS.
